lead_paragraph: Hideki Matsuyama edged American Rickie Fowler in a playoff at the Phoenix Open on Sunday to become only the second Japanese player with multiple wins on the PGA Tour.

headline.print_headline: Matsuyama Rallies to Beat Fowler in Phoenix Open Playoff
